# Keep the build context small and host-agnostic. Never ship host node_modules
# (wrong arch + huge) or build artifacts — the image installs deps fresh.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/test-results
**/playwright-report

# VCS, tooling, and local-only scratch.
.git
.github
.claude
.worktrees
.superpowers
**/.DS_Store

# Secrets and env files must never enter an image layer.
**/.env*

# Docs and plans aren't needed at runtime.
docs
README.md
